  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[When Digivolving] By placing 1 Digimon on top of its owner''s
    security stack, reveal all of your opponent''s security cards, and place 1 card
    among them on top of your opponent''s deck. Shuffle the rest and return them
    to the security stack.

    [Start of Opponent''s Turn] Declare 1 card category.
    Then, reveal the top card of your opponent''s deck. If it''s of that category,
    this Digimon isn''t affected by that category''s effects, other than this Digimon''s
    effects, for the turn. Return the revealed cards to the top or bottom of your
    opponent''s deck.'
